               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Asmat Prayer for forgiveness of the soul and healing of the flesh, ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="24v" facs="002">Fols 1r–24v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-qǝddus Hǝryāqos za-hagara Bǝhnǝsā</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="25r" to="76v" facs="026">Fols 25r–76v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer for forgiveness of the soul and healing of the flesh, ‎‎<foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡</foreign>‎</title>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                        <locus from="25r" to="29r" facs="026">Fols 25r–29r</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Monday, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘሰኑይ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡ ወመንጽሔ፡ ኃጢአት፡ አፍናኤል፡ አቅናኤል፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                        <locus from="29r" to="37v" facs="030">Fols 29r–37v</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Tuesday, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘሠሉስ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ወይቤልዎ፡ መላእክት፡ ታስተኃፍሮሙኑ፡ ለእለ፡ ደገምዎ፡ በበ፯ ጊዜ፡ ወይቤሎሙ፡</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                        <locus from="37v" to="43v" facs="039">Fols 37v–43v</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Wednesday,  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘረቡዕ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ይቀድሰኒ፡ አስማቲሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ሴድላዊ፡ በድጋዊ፡ ቄድሎ፡</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4">
                        <locus from="43v" to="52r" facs="045">Fols 43v–52r</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Thursday, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘሐሙስ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎ሥርየተ፡ እምነቶሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ወለኵሎሙ፤ ፸ወ፪አርድእት፡ ከማሁ፡ ይቤሎሙ፡</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5">
                        <locus from="52r" to="66r" facs="053">Fols 52r–66r</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Friday, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘዓርብ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየተ፡ ኃጢአት፡ ዘሰዓሉ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚኦሙ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6">
                        <locus from="66r" to="73r" facs="067">Fols 66r–73r</locus>
                        <title>Prayers for Saturday, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘቀዳሚት፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">:  በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ዘሀሎ፡ ውስተ፡ ንዑሰ፡ ወንጌል፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ነገረ፡ማርያም፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7">
                        <locus from="73r" to="73v" facs="074">Fols 73r–73v, </locus>
                        <locus from="76r" to="76v" facs="077">76r–76v</locus>
                        <title>Sunday Reading, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘእሁድ፡</foreign>
                        </title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየተ፡ ኃጢአት፡ ዘሰዓሉ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚኦሙ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                    <note>
                        <locus from="74r" to="75v" facs="075">Fols 74r–75v</locus> is a misplaced sheet elsewhere within the asmat prayers
                      </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
